EASEL ON


                  Combined Balance Option - Help

    Used to qualify a relationship based on all combined
    balances meeting a required balance, or either of one of
    four combined balances meeting a required balance.  If only
    one of the Combined Balance Category Codes is defined in
    the model, than this option is ignored.  Valid entries are:

      A  All combined balance requirements must be met.
      O  One combined balance requirement must be met.
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M01056S

EASEL OFF
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
FIELD=PFKEY,    PIC='X(01)', ATTR=(DISPLAY,HIDDEN)
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
